name: Humpback Whale Evolution | Blue Fish Orca Clicker
name_original: Humpback Whale Evolution | Blue Fish Orca Clicker
description:
What happens to an ordinary humpback whale when mutations start taking place? Combine whales to evolve them and discover their most curious, exotic and bizarre forms.

> Tap to knock out other whales
> Tap again to absorb them
> Gain experience and evolve
> Read about your evolutions
